EM_Ajaxproducts

Support Version: 1.6 , 1.7 , 1.8
Day Update : Feb 7 2017
------------------------------------
How to Install

1. Extract the zip file to EM_Ajaxproducts folder. 
2. Upload all files and sub-directories inside the main folder EM_Ajaxproducts on your magento root folder. Select overwrite all if asked.
3. Login to your Magento backend, disable all magento cache, flush cache and refresh your website again.
4. EM_Ajaxproducts magento extension will be installed automatically once your website is reloaded.